msgid "Requirement 12: maintain a policy that addresses information security for all personnel"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: security_pcidss.xml:1395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any organization that handles valuable information should have a general security policy. All relevant aspects should be included to make it clear for employees and stakeholders what the possible risks are and how to avoid them."
msgstr ""

